# Privacy Policy for Voca

**Last updated:** January 15, 2025

## Overview

Voca ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our AI personal assistant app for iPhone and Apple Watch handles information.

## Information We Collect

**We do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information.**

- **No Account Required:** Voca does not require user registration or accounts
- **No Personal Data Collection:** We do not collect names, email addresses, phone numbers, or other personal identifiers
- **No Usage Analytics:** We do not track how you use the app
- **No Location Data:** We do not access or store location information

## How Your Data Is Handled

### Conversation Data
- All conversations are stored **locally** on your device
- Conversation history can be cleared at any time
- We do not have access to your conversations
- Data is protected by iOS/watchOS security features

### Voice Input
- Voice input is processed using Apple's Speech framework
- Voice data follows Apple's privacy guidelines
- No voice recordings are stored by our app

### AI Service Communication
- When you send messages, they are transmitted to AI service providers
- This communication is secured using standard HTTPS encryption
- AI service privacy policies apply to data sent to their servers
- We recommend reviewing your AI service provider's privacy policy

## Data Security

- All local data is protected by iOS/watchOS security features
- Network communications use industry-standard HTTPS encryption
- No advertising networks or third-party analytics
- No data monetization or selling

## Third-Party Services

Voca may integrate with AI service providers to deliver responses. When you use these features:

- Your messages are sent to the AI service provider
- Data handling is governed by the AI provider's privacy policy
- We do not store or access responses from AI services

## Children's Privacy

Our app does not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided personal information, please contact us.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any material changes by updating the "Last updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy.

## Your Rights

Since we do not collect personal data, there is no personal data to access, modify, or delete from our servers. You can clear all local data by deleting and reinstalling the app.

---

*This privacy policy is designed to be transparent about our data practices and ensure user privacy protection.*
